### E-Commerce API - POST Endpoints Test Suite
### Usar con la extensión REST Client de VS Code
### Orden recomendado: ejecutar de arriba hacia abajo (respeta dependencias entre entidades)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

# ============================================================
# 1. USUARIOS - Sin dependencias
# ============================================================

### Crear usuario cliente
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "juan.perez",
  "email": "juan.perez@email.com",
  "passwordHash": "hashed_password_123",
  "firstName": "Juan",
  "lastName": "Perez",
  "role": "CUSTOMER",
  "phone": "+5491155554444"
}

###

### Crear usuario admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin.garcia",
  "email": "admin@tienda.com",
  "passwordHash": "admin_hashed_456",
  "firstName": "Carlos",
  "lastName": "Garcia",
  "role": "ADMIN",
  "phone": "+5491166667777"
}

###

# ============================================================
# 2. DEPOSITOS - Sin dependencias
# ============================================================

### Crear depósito principal
POST {{baseUrl}}/warehouses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Deposito Central Buenos Aires",
  "location": "Av. Lugones 1234, CABA",
  "contactPhone": "+5491100001111"
}

###

### Crear depósito secundario
POST {{baseUrl}}/warehouses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Deposito Zona Sur",
  "location": "Calle Falsa 742, Lomas de Zamora",
  "contactPhone": "+5491122223333"
}

###

# ============================================================
# 3. CATEGORIAS - Sin dependencias
# ============================================================

### Crear categoría Electrónica
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Electrónica y tecnología"
}

###

### Crear categoría Ropa
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Indumentaria y accesorios"
}

###

### Crear categoría Hogar
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Artículos para el hogar"
}

###

# ============================================================
# 4. DIRECCIONES - Requiere: userId existente (ej: 1)
# ============================================================

### Crear dirección para usuario 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/addresses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "street": "Av. Corrientes 1500",
  "city": "Buenos Aires",
  "state": "CABA",
  "zipCode": "1043",
  "referenceNote": "Piso 3, depto B. Timbre apellido Perez"
}

###

### Crear segunda dirección para usuario 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/addresses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "street": "Calle Rivadavia 800",
  "city": "Córdoba",
  "state": "Córdoba",
  "zipCode": "5000",
  "referenceNote": "Casa con portón verde"
}

###

# ============================================================
# 5. PRODUCTOS - Requiere: categoryId existente (ej: 1)
# ============================================================

### Crear producto: Notebook
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Notebook Lenovo IdeaPad 15",
  "description": "Notebook 15.6\" Intel Core i5, 16GB RAM, 512GB SSD",
  "brand": "Lenovo",
  "categoryId": 1
}

###

### Crear producto: Smartphone
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Samsung Galaxy A54",
  "description": "Smartphone 6.4\" AMOLED, 128GB, cámara triple",
  "brand": "Samsung",
  "categoryId": 1
}

###

### Crear producto: Remera
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Remera Algodón Premium",
  "description": "Remera 100% algodón, corte recto",
  "brand": "BasicWear",
  "categoryId": 2
}

###

# ============================================================
# 6. VARIANTES DE PRODUCTO - Requiere: productId existente (ej: 1)
# ============================================================

### Crear variante de notebook (color negro)
POST {{baseUrl}}/variants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "sku": "LENOVO-IDEAPAD15-BLK",
  "attributes": "{\"color\": \"Negro\", \"ram\": \"16GB\", \"storage\": \"512GB\"}",
  "basePrice": 850000.00
}

###

### Crear variante de notebook (color gris)
POST {{baseUrl}}/variants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "sku": "LENOVO-IDEAPAD15-GRY",
  "attributes": "{\"color\": \"Gris\", \"ram\": \"16GB\", \"storage\": \"512GB\"}",
  "basePrice": 850000.00
}

###

### Crear variante de remera (talle M, rojo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/variants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 3,
  "sku": "BASICWEAR-REMERA-M-RED",
  "attributes": "{\"talle\": \"M\", \"color\": \"Rojo\"}",
  "basePrice": 12500.00
}

###

# ============================================================
# 7. INVENTARIO - Requiere: variantId y warehouseId existentes
# ============================================================

### Cargar stock: variante 1 en depósito 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/inventory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": 1,
  "warehouseId": 1,
  "stockQuantity": 50
}

###

### Cargar stock: variante 2 en depósito 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/inventory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": 2,
  "warehouseId": 2,
  "stockQuantity": 30
}

###

### Cargar stock: variante 3 (remera) en depósito 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/inventory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": 3,
  "warehouseId": 1,
  "stockQuantity": 200
}

###

# ============================================================
# 8. PEDIDOS - Requiere: userId y shippingAddressId existentes
# ============================================================

### Crear pedido para usuario 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "shippingAddressId": 1,
  "status": "PENDING"
}

###

### Crear pedido confirmado para usuario 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "shippingAddressId": 2,
  "status": "CONFIRMED"
}

###

# ============================================================
# 9. PAGOS - Requiere: orderId existente (ej: 1)
# ============================================================

### Registrar pago con tarjeta de crédito
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "paymentMethod": "CREDIT_CARD",
  "transactionId": "TXN-CC-20240410-001",
  "paymentStatus": "APPROVED"
}

###

### Registrar pago con transferencia bancaria
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 2,
  "paymentMethod": "BANK_TRANSFER",
  "transactionId": "TXN-BT-20240410-002",
  "paymentStatus": "PENDING"
}

###

# ============================================================
# 10. ENTREGAS - Requiere: orderId existente (ej: 1)
# ============================================================

### Registrar entrega con envío estándar
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliveries
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "shippingMethod": "STANDARD",
  "trackingNumber": "AR123456789",
  "deliveryStatus": "DISPATCHED"
}

###

### Registrar entrega con envío express
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliveries
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 2,
  "shippingMethod": "EXPRESS",
  "trackingNumber": "AR987654321",
  "deliveryStatus": "IN_TRANSIT"
}

###

# ============================================================
# 11. DEVOLUCIONES - Requiere: orderId existente (ej: 1)
# ============================================================

### Registrar devolución por producto defectuoso
POST {{baseUrl}}/returns
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "reason": "Producto llegó con pantalla rota",
  "status": "PENDING"
}

###

### Registrar devolución por error en el pedido
POST {{baseUrl}}/returns
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 2,
  "reason": "Recibí un color diferente al pedido",
  "status": "APPROVED"
}

###

# ============================================================
# 12. RESEÑAS - Requiere: userId y productId existentes
# ============================================================

### Crear reseña positiva
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "productId": 1,
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Excelente notebook, muy rápida y buena batería. Llegó en perfecto estado."
}

###

### Crear reseña neutral
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "productId": 2,
  "rating": 3,
  "comment": "Producto correcto pero la entrega tardó más de lo esperado."
}

###
